.SS "napi-build-utils"
A set of utilities to assist developers of tools that build \fRN-API\fP native add-ons\&.
.PP
The main repository can be found \fRhere\fP\&.
.PP
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBnapi-build-utils\fP
