.IP "  \(bu" 4
\fB\&.logUnsupportedVersion(napiVersion, log)\fP
.IP "  \(bu" 4
\fB\&.getBestNapiBuildVersion()\fP ⇒ \fRnumber\fP | \fRundefined\fP
.IP "  \(bu" 4
\fB\&.getNapiBuildVersions()\fP ⇒ \fRArray\&.<string>\fP
